, sermons, letters—from a new perspective in order to understand how power and resistance shaped religious identities in the later Roman Empire.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 31. Jan 2022) 7aRELIGION / Judaism / General.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978150362398940uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781503623989423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781503623989/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles